file_content.text: Force field is up, Cipher! Go--run!
Slicing into the ray shield controls now!
We're almost there, Cipher! Just a little more...
I still need more power to get that force field up!
Uploading bridge schematics. You'll need to take out these components to reroute power to the force fields!
Keep him distracted, and I can raise the force field!
Nothing you can do can destroy me.
I sense your fear. I sense your plan!
You think you know what I am capable of?
